title: God Bless Football: Jason Taylor & Chip Kelly
description:
A wonderful smelling, Miami Dolphins legend and Hall of Famer, Jason Taylor, joins the show! (8:28). Chip Kelly get us ready for UCLA vs. Oregon and might have positions on his staff for Stugotz, Billy and Jessica (21:32). Chris Simms previews week 7 and is tired of being disrespected by a member of the show (34:26). Stu-Ya-Gotz (52:03). Mike Golic gets surprised by an NFL head coach and ranks the members of the show (55:29). Chris, Joba and K-Funk make their weekly picks (1:12:21). Carl Douglas crashes the party to make his picks and promises big guests next week!.
